<section class="about-intro">
  <div class="about-intro-inner container">
    <div class="about-intro-text reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
      <h2>Made for Spaces That Mean Something</h2>
      <p>MUNLER was founded on a single conviction: that the objects we choose to live with should be worth choosing. Not mass-produced. Not compromised. Not temporary.</p>
      <p>We design and manufacture stainless steel mirrors and home objects that are built to last — using ecological glass, precision-engineered frames, and a level of finish that most furniture brands reserve for their most expensive pieces.</p>
      <p>Every MUNLER piece is conceived in the UK and manufactured to exacting specifications. We use grade 304 brushed stainless steel — the same standard used in professional kitchens and architectural interiors — because we believe the materials in your home deserve the same rigour as those in a building designed to last a century.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-intro-img reveal">
      <img src="https://munler.co.uk/cdn/shop/files/bu_odanin_farkli_shotlarini_ver__202605231515_91bb8878-aaa5-4548-a64a-2a5e1238b6b5.jpg" alt="MUNLER — The Brook Mirror">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

